11:22.020 --> 11:22.830
[Pertunjukan Musik Jaz Shanghai Klasik]

11:22.850 --> 11:23.660
[Musik Jaz Paman Tua]

11:23.690 --> 11:24.800
[Paling Berkelas di Shanghai]

11:26.210 --> 11:26.530
[Komentar]

11:26.550 --> 11:27.210
[Ini pertunjukan di mana?]

11:27.210 --> 11:27.570
